<P>
FUND-RAISER OF MUSIC, COMEDY SET FOR JULY 23 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Comedian George Lopez, musicians Marcos Loya and Francisco Gonzalez, 
playwright/performance artist Luis Alfaro and Andean music group Alturas will 
perform "Una Noche del Teatro '94" at South Coast Repertory in Costa Mesa on 
July 23. 
</P>
<P>
 The evening of comedy and music will benefit the company's local outreach 
programs and Hispanic Playwrights Project. Tickets are $35 and $100. 
Information: (714) 957-2602, Ext. 223. 
</P>
