vitriol, against all these absurd suits thrown at them, may I ask who is paying 
the bills for Paula Jones' complaint? She, too, has to pay lawyers, and since 
she had no great amount of money, if any at all, someone is paying her bills to 
harass the Clintons. Must those people, who obviously are not Democrats, stay 
unnamed? 
</P>
<P>
 JACK P. GABRIEL 
