<P>
 Movie star Arnold Schwarzenegger will play host at a charity auction at 8 p.m. 
Wednesday at Planet Hollywood, the restaurant he co-owns at South Coast Plaza 
Village, 1641 W. Sunflower Ave. in Santa Ana. 
</P>
<P>
 The live auction will feature clothes worn by motion picture celebrities as 
