 Incognito, at the Diamond Club, 7070 Hollywood Blvd., Hollywood. An 
alternative twist is given to sketch comedy, character acts and improv. Every 
Thursday at 8 p.m. $5 admission. Information: (213) 969-8322. 
</P>
