 Klub Uvula, at the Variety Arts Center, 940 S. Figueroa St., Los Angeles. A 
wide range of entertainment includes alternative stand-up and improv. Every 
Saturday at 9 p.m. $12.50 admission. Information: (213) 368-8958. 
